//! MCP Stdio Server - {{ server_name }}
//!
//! Generated by ggen from ontology: {{ ontology_path }}
//! Core axiom: A = μ(O), μ ∘ μ = μ, hash(A) = hash(μ(O)), O ⊨ Σ
//!
//! This server implements the Model Context Protocol (MCP) over stdio,
//! enabling communication with LLM clients through standardized JSON-RPC 2.0.
//!
//! ## Features
//!
//! - Tool registration and invocation
//! - Resource management (read/write)
//! - Prompt templates
//! - ZAI streaming support
//! - A2A message bridging
//!
//! ## Protocol
//!
//! Uses JSON-RPC 2.0 over stdin/stdout with line-delimited JSON messages.

